WEBVTT

00:01:26.522 --> 00:01:31.071
pahali ambapo wanawake wanaachwa wafe
nje ya manyumba yao

00:01:31.095 --> 00:01:33.683
kwa sababu ya kuzungumza na mwanaume
kwa rununu

00:01:33.707 --> 00:01:35.577
wakisinzia ni "heshima ya familia."

00:01:36.158 --> 00:01:37.929
Wacha niseme hivi bayana:

00:01:38.681 --> 00:01:40.146
siyo heshima;

00:01:40.170 --> 00:01:42.526
hayo ni mauaji.

00:01:45.551 --> 00:01:49.702
Mimi natokea kijiji kidogo
sana pale Punjab, Pakistani

00:01:49.726 --> 00:01:54.600
pahali ambapo wanawake hawaruhusiwi 
kuendelea na masomo ya juu.

00:01:55.308 --> 00:01:59.022
Wakubwa wa jamaa yangu 
hawakuwaruhusu wanawake wao

00:01:59.046 --> 00:02:02.908
waendelee na masomo ya juu 
ama taaluma zao.